---
title: Garlic Chicken & Mash with Steamed Veggies & Truffle Mayo
description: Every now and then it’s nice to go back to basics. They always carry a sense of nostalgia with them. Allow all the memories of
cosy family dinners to flow in when you bite into this tender chicken, seasoned with fresh herbs, a potato mash and veggies.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
